test_1005,3,3,I mostly just like being outdoors. I love the scenery and the clean air. 
test_1005,3,4,"The scenery is the best, especially in the fall when the leaves change.  Do your grand kids like to roast marshmallows over the fire?  "
test_1005,3,5,"Oh absolutely. That's one of their fun things to do when camping. Yes I agree, the changing leaves and cooler temperatures make fall the best time to camp and hike. Do you take your dog with you when you hike?"
test_1005,3,6,Yeah he loves going on hikes.
test_1005,3,7,We used to have a dog and I know the grandkids would love it if we got another one but I'm not sure if I'm ready. 
test_1005,3,8,"Dogs are a ton of work so you definitely need to make sure your ready for one again.  But they do make the companions.  If you were to get one, what kind would you get?"
