test_1014,3,7,Oh that's amazing!! Never been to Poland. I should go to Italy soon... but I would love to visit new places to be honest. 
test_1014,3,8,Is your family still in Italy? I have been to Venice a few years ago. It was stunning!
test_1014,3,9,"Oh yes, Venice is a must go to place :)) Yes my family is still in Italy. Rome. Have you been there?"
test_1014,3,10,I haven't but it is on my bucket list. I love traveling and getting to know different cultures and traditions. I also love trying new foods and of course tasting coffee.
test_1014,3,11,I hope you tried Italian coffee when you went to Venice! :)
