test_268,4,0,have you though more about owning a horse?
test_268,4,1,"Yes, I have.  I still think it doesn't make sense unless I leave the city.  I'm also thinking about what it means from a psychological perspective.  I wonder if my thinking about horses a lot is Freudian or something."
