test_273,4,0,So how is it going with your new book about reptiles?
test_273,4,1,"I am still in the research phase of the project.  I think it is going slower than my usual projects because I'm a little creeped out by reptiles...lol.  A bearded dragon sounds kind of cool, though.  What are they like as pets?"
test_273,4,2,"Well, since they're reptiles, you can just keep them in an aquarium. Very easy to lost track of if you let them roam around. All in all, pretty low maintenance. Maybe your book idea could desensitize kids to reptiles! "
